item.title: What the f is this
item.dc:creator: @beats beats
item.description:
@beats wrote:

[quote=“OGolemX, post:11, topic:486446”]@echo off
title Vistex Client

color B
cd Flow
echo Starting
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_13\bin\java.exe” -Xmx300m ShowMessageDialog
pause

lol… change it to the path where your jdk is.
open your computer, go look for programfiles or programfiles (x86)
and inside one of them it will say java
look in to those files and look at ur jdk version

so if your jdk was 7 and it was inside program files (x86)
your code would be like this

@echo off
title Vistex Client

color B
cd Flow
echo Starting
“C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.7.0\bin\java.exe” -Xmx300m ShowMessageDialog
pause[/quote]
lol i changed my version my jdk version

Host Gushers:

Ok, i see that this is trisidiax v3, so what u need to do is click on popout client, if u continue to need help, contact me on skype @ rspsdesigner.
